Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:19.53,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:25.35,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沒有星光的迷宮裡掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:30.38,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨的少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.95,0:00:36.10,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受靈魂的吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:41.35,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宇宙正在呼喚你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.30,0:00:47.15,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背負傷痕 知曉孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:52.50,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於明白了羈絆的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:00:55.36,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除陰翳眼眸中的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:57.99,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不安和困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:04.50,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:08.33,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士們 站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:11.00,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:14.42,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果背負的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:16.35,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠稱為愛的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:19.05,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士們相互支持
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:21.68,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化為風的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:26.15,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全新的Ω神話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:31.40,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就從現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:21.00,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光榮字幕組&galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.85,0:01:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超必殺 幻影之爪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.68,0:01:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的埃吉爾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太過輕視黃金聖鬥士 天秤座玄武了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.23,0:02:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.82,0:02:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃金聖衣居然如此牢固？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟讓我蒙羞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許珀裡翁大人的聖劍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要借我使用麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是聖劍？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個小宇宙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從劍裡散發出來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這散發出偉大的小宇宙的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.94,0:02:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其名為 天地崩滅斬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是自神話時代起就流傳下來的眾神的聖劍之一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此劍一揮便可崩天裂地 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.23,0:03:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃是滅絕一切的破壞之劍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一級刻鬥士 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四天王許珀裡翁大人的佩劍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說許珀裡翁？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許珀裡翁大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我埃吉爾將感恩戴德地使用天地崩滅斬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任你劍 箭 還是火槍 儘管來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為掌管均衡與和諧的黃金聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我天秤座玄武是不會被打敗的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可難說了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也已經發覺了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這其中壓倒一切的攻擊性的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是何等強大而不祥的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陣型不要亂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小宇宙好強大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去Palaestra會被毀滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榮斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被這把劍散發出的和阿普斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 比那更強大的小宇宙所摧毀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天地崩滅斬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅違抗帕拉斯大人的聖鬥士們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄武的死鬥！聖劍對天秤之劍！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宇宙居然可以燃燒到這等地步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀天滅地之力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不堪一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一擊致命嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是許珀裡翁大人的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可劈斬一切的破壞之劍 天地崩滅斬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抹殺聖鬥士 只憑一把劍就足夠了嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許珀裡翁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.09,0:05:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就無需我出場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃金聖鬥士之流 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我偉大的聖劍面前 將如塵埃般灰飛煙滅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天秤座黃金聖鬥士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想讓你也看到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這天地崩滅斬之下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士悉數橫死的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬座
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再讓你向前一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可愛的學弟學妹們都在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能讓你通過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是弒神並擊敗黃金的你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能打敗身為二級刻鬥士的我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對付你們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不需要借助一級刻鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四天王許珀裡翁大人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一級…刻鬥士？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是相當於聖鬥士中的黃金聖鬥士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一級的力量可以輕鬆凌駕於黃金聖鬥士之上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻鬥士的水準和你們這些聖鬥士可不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看天秤座的屍身 就清楚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說誰的屍身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 吃了天地崩滅斬的攻擊還…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看黃金聖衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是有著圓盾的天秤座聖衣 怎可能會被擊破
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄武先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何你們會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓你們出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:08:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別礙事 這傢伙是我的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了別礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是叫埃吉爾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打就來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著你那天地崩滅斬的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 我不會讓你渡過此橋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要渡過的 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:22.66,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三途河，冥界河名，相傳為生死分界，在此前的聖鬥士篇章中有所涉及
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是三途河！     
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橋什麼的根本無須渡過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來告訴你吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天地崩滅斬的恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此劍將斬斷和破碎時空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拭目以待吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天地崩滅斬是可以斬斷時間邏輯的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的時間啊 停止吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時光毀滅（Chrono Destruction）！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的小宇宙消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是停止了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什麼 埃吉爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我破壞了所有事物的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然 你這傢伙似乎被黃金聖衣保護了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這些傢伙的時間已經被這把劍奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾呢 你沒能保護Palaestra
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宇宙！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很微弱…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家還…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不能動 卻還擁有意識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為受到從聖衣石中新生的聖衣的保護嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.01,0:10:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這傢伙怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為受到了天馬座的保護
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是潛在的小宇宙特別強大？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打倒奪走時間的刻鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能恢復原狀了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是簡單易懂的規則呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為你能打倒我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一招就讓你親身體驗這把劍的厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會如你所願嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天秤座的聖衣中包括圓盾在內 有六種武器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:11:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拐 雙節棍 三節棍 槍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及天秤之劍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士禁止使用武器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非雅典娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或天秤座聖鬥士下達許可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能使用這武器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星光環繞的天秤聖衣之劍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾師童虎 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您所傳授給我的天秤座武器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我一用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:48.09,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激戰！聖劍與天秤之劍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接我一劍吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.81,0:12:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守護雅典娜的黃金聖鬥士 天秤之劍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 那破玩意在這天地崩滅斬面前和把鈍刀無異
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我怎麼斬斷它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能接住這天地崩滅斬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看這個能粉碎星辰的天秤之劍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.39,0:12:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 看樣子雙劍相交時所釋放出的巨大小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算劍能承受 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃金聖衣也不能完全抵禦天地崩滅斬的衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身體已經受到了損傷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:13:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經毫無勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死在許珀裡翁大人的面前吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師 師父
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾師童虎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我常被您說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我是個沒有毅力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡倒下的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對師父也好 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對年輕的聖鬥士也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都無法做出榜樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為何要站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了將師父的遺志傳遞給年輕的聖鬥士們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少裝帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾師童虎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我的師兄紫龍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像他們為了同伴拼上性命一次次站起來那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算犧牲性命 我也要保護這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 在這天地崩滅斬面前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的聖鬥士都將滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就給你最後一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 真是不像樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站著就升天了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還揚言說要保護青銅聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就只剩粉碎剩下的聖鬥士了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你選擇了愚蠢地白白送死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拔 拔不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 你挨了這天地崩滅斬還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我玄武不會白死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這把劍可不是為了打敗你而出鞘的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本沒把你放在眼裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的對手從一開始 便是位於這把劍另一端的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要毀掉這把劍 大家就能復原
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我這天秤座之劍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.89,0:16:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難 難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為了毀掉天地崩滅斬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才用自己的身體接住了劍不成？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少以我的性命作交換 摧毀這把劍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕的聖鬥士們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼承我之靈魂 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消滅強大的邪惡勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾師童虎的遺志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我繼承了天秤座聖衣一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士在新的時代 應建立起自己的意志並將它托付給下一代
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許珀裡翁 你的劍就由我玄武收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廬山昇天霸！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是無法破壞它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能感覺到 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的小宇宙正在恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:17:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄武先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄武先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃吉爾 你手持吾劍應戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還落得這般田地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.26,0:18:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過能除掉一名黃金聖鬥士 結果也算差強人意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼回去 肯定會被問罪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓許珀裡翁大人借與我的劍出現傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許珀裡翁大人定會盛怒不已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會饒了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能幹掉他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弒神的光牙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.65,0:18:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能奉上這小子的首級！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄武 你的意志 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.96,0:19:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經確確實實
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確確實實地感受到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙君！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打爆他！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.88,0:19:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙的小宇宙燃起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.59,0:19:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…這…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.67,0:19:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛…虛張聲勢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃我這招 超必殺 幻影之爪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬流星拳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃吉爾大人被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快撤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄武
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得漂亮 光牙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟能打倒他…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄武先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別大驚小怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是我的守護星座的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本說過有時間要與你好好交談的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.48,0:20:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我食言了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.32,0:20:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.76,0:20:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的戰鬥和小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經向我訴說了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從您身上受益良多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.08,0:20:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深得您之教誨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 我的師父就是 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父親紫龍和天秤座玄武您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:20:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍峰…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄武
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.64,0:21:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要相信你自己的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄武
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你們 一定能夠覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺醒Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ω？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的話 一定可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄武
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.67,0:21:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄武先生——！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄武 你的死一定會激起軒然大波
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.01,0:21:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的小宇宙一定能夠讓聖鬥士們行動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.76,0:22:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天秤座的黃金聖鬥士玄武之死所帶來的衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.20,0:22:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿是要更進一步緊逼陷入不安中的聖鬥士們而出現的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射手座的星矢 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.22,0:22:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及女神雅典娜 終於降臨戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的反擊從現在才開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.90,0:22:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 聖鬥士星矢Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.16,0:22:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢，出陣！雅典娜的決意！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾感受到小宇宙的存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
